data.description: Location location!!! Call this property your home in Austin Texas, known as the Live Music Capital of the World. Like to golf? The Roy Kizer Golf Course is just around the corner as is McKinney Falls State Park. Live close by all the attractions in this adorable 3/2 with your own outdoor entertainment. Swimming pool and oversized corner lot. This large yard make this house the central location for your social events. Large living room, open kitchen with gas range. Nice & bright throughout with lots of windows & sky lights in home. This floorpan offers nice size rooms, good storage, ceiling fans in every room, an abundance of cabinet space in kitchen, French doors to pool and outdoor area. Just a little Austin gem of a home. Book your tour today and call this property your new home.
